    public class ConnectionGraph
extends org.jgrapht.graph.DirectedMultigraph<NodeStack,Requirement>
    This Graph represents all Connections between NodeStacks

    The graph basically represents a contracted version (A Node Stack is one Vertex) of the Effective Models Graph It can easily be extended to also handle other types of relationships
